Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫How do you still create\Na relationship each other♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s my awkward friend’s fault♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone somewhere\Nto embrace me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫While the devil is not here\Nand between the chaos♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now,\NI’m trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’ll see I’m always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and your roller coaster\Ninside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and\Nthe unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫To pierce with the theory♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun\Ngoes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and the theory in the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,THE YEARNING IN SLUMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been here for over 2000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, we need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to destroy the Kunad Gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we need you help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back at Arahabaki's secure site,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you used the Red Strings to jump through time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to 2000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That created a dimensional entanglement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the entanglement exists,\Nthe Kunad Gate will not disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the whole world will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you to undo it and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It cannot be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the person who formed\Nthe dimensional entanglement can undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, so it is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So why won't you help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot undo it.\NThat's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, you traveled back in time to save Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would you go back to 2000 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo Sumeragi could be\Na wielder of Red Strings too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I was drawn by his beckoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You went back to 2000 years ago by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for a way to save Alice 2000 years from then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,a way to change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the answer you've found\Nwas to become Yakumo Sumeragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I assume the identity of the founding father,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there must have been something I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,there is only one way to save Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I must connect myself to Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By connecting myself to\Nall the system mainframes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can alter history.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can save Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That can only mean Arahabaki is a\Nbio-computer made from human brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you who forcefully
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,invaded our brains?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But whatever the case is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I've tried so\Nhard time and time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Time and time again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The person I was not
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,jumped through time repeatedly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and became Yakumo Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The dimensional entanglement was formed\Nbecause of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem cannot be solved\Neven if I undo the entanglement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will create new entanglements!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen is two people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my question for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me becoming Yakumo Sumeragi\Nand connecting with Arahabaki
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,were the only way to save Alice's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Jumping through time, remaining in Arahabaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the trial and error proved\Nthat was the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So why can't I travel 2000 years back in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did the time jump fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've given you my aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me everything you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your memories!\NI'll consume everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been absorbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what he meant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,by connecting with Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All those memories are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-What is...\N-Are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you acquired new information\Nabout Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite hundreds...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thousands...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,One of tens of thousands...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The me aside from myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,how many times I've given\Nthe same information to my other selves?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, the future can't be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The only person who has realized it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,was me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You are just wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You will get nothing out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You are just one of many in the endless cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I must save Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I try,\NI must save Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, hand over the Red Strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your time jump failed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because you couldn't copy Yuito's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with your power,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's impossible for you to wield\Nthe Red Strings for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why you need to\Nkeep copying their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your resistance is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Me acquiring the Red Strings from you\Nis the inevitable outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Time jump will destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will travel through time once again
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,by any means necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You refuse to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka and the Moon\Nhave many dirty secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but destroying the world\Nwill not resolve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We must create a new future for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The world built upon history of dirty secrets\Nis worth nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will change the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make it happen this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you want to save Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if you understand or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,His power has been increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you just abandon that which is dear to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After going through their harsh\Nand challenging training,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the Scarlet Guardians that will\Nprotect the planet has arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the Scarlet Guardians are none\Nother than the two young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Private Yuito Sumeragi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,versus Private Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. The weather looks nice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's been your ambition\Nto join the OSF all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go out and take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a place I want to check out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to go back in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so you could save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was you, Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was you, Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you could have saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the regret eating away at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Back at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,had you realized the threat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have turned into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The regret must be eating away at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost contact with him\Nafter he was sent to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Had you come looking for me,\NI would still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a voice that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted me to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated fighting, it disgusted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so afraid, but I couldn't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You are right, I regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the slightest difference
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is enough to create a different future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter where we are,\Nwe can only make one choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Making choices and moving forward\Nis part of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the only thing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, we must make the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you set aside important matters
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,over your own selfish desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your yearning is nothing but a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It was because of Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking like you know everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all because of Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not just Nagi's pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't turn a blind eye to people's suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't change the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We must move toward the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We must do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,These are just excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandoning your past,\Ndenying the tragedy that had taken place,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you are running away from the problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I will save Alice no matter what the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a future\NAlice wanted for you to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice wouldn't want you to destroy the world\Njust to save her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare say her name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see it by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You are already connected to Arahabaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what Alice wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not change my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not change my mind now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over your Red Strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,After I get the Red Strings from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,both of you will be useless to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, do what Karen just did!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Search for the memory inside Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Search for the real Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have been a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you miss her so much\Nsays everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always stuck his neck out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And just now, he must have
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,suffered some serious injuries because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't want his help,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but I want him to love himself more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have him by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I need to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, it won't stop him\Nfrom risking his life for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the more reasons to work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To make sure Karen won't\Nbe worried about me again,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I must work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I want Karen to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen Travers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never agree with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never agree with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've copied your Red Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I can finally make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know what Alice really wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I must save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, it's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm troubled by my own yearning♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Unveil the blocked sun ray♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's a stranger in me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫That I've never seen♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I can not soar in the sky without fear♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm spreading my wings♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Dancing gracefully like a bird♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And gazing towards the scarlet sky♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I chased after the gust♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The scenery spreads into\Nthe ever-changing world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Inside the intertwined brilliance♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm still searching for tomorrow's direction♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Tomorrow's in your hands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don't tell me now you're afraid♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's no time to waste♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Go forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Have no fear for anything♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Now, let's go♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Into a brand new day♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,OPERATION KUNAD GATE
